following his uncles wish he resigned from the navy in and joined the austro hungarian foreign office at the end of november odo received_orders to leave for mexico as charg_daffaires the austrian minister had been absent from mexico city since early in and odo had the ungrateful task of creating order out of chaos a condition aggravated by the revolution in that unhappy country
