 a long rest at the loomis ranch the stades took up residence in topanga where odo began writing again encouraged by early successes in at which time he had sold numerous short_stories and epigrams to hl mencken then editor of smart set magazine during the next ten years odo wrote numerous short_stories novelettes two novels and in collaboration with edgecumb pinchon the biography viva villa which was sold to the mgm studios and as a motion_picture_achieved_a_considerable_success being nominated for best picture in the academy awards in and earning million for mgm by the late s
